579	21	Music major	Male	To test the effects of negative and positive conditioning around a person on a subject's unconscious or implicit bias system? In other words, you wanted to see whether you could convince us (through sheer brute force) that someone was bad or good and whether such assocation, if successful, could become automatic. There are also other elements in here, such as muscle-memory association and (if you plan to measure this) the potency of an initial impression -- in this case, nice Bob.	-